  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, OK, that's the-- the situation I was in-- in process to describe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't finish, but maybe I will answer you after finishing this-- this episode.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when she was-- when Liliana was at this apartment, and the cleaning lady was coming, sometimes she asked her son, a grown up son, to come and help her with-- to dispose something and so on.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's the-- the way how this son of that cleaning woman have seen Lillian, and he had the version, official version that is the-- the rich peasant, Polish peasant daughter hiding there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When-- [SIGHS] when we were at this yard, and this new transport came from Warsaw, and this man was that son of that cleaning woman.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, logically, we-- we knew something right away, following-- you know, that there is something fishy with her and her version while she was living in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's why Liliana said to me that we are lost because she suspected that maybe this boy will put 1 and 2 together-- and together, and will come to the conclusion that probably me or-- or her who are Jewish people, and therefore, we were in jeopardy.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So shortly speaking, after that, we decided to run away from that place, from the Kapfenberg.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Luckily, we had already some acquaintance, some Polish man, who was already working, but who came from Vienna.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he had some connections in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, not telling him the truth, only that we don't want to stay in Kapfenberg because we cannot get [SIGHS] some kind of-- of-- of housing together.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we are just living and going to Vienna and looking for-- in Vienna for some solution for us.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
